Summary: three solid black eggs together forming a triangle with small white spot in center
divs: Sighting DetailsI was on my back porch, smoking a cig. from the south a solid black oject was coming under the clouds it was shaped like three black eggs or footballs bunched together forming a triangle..about as high as a small plane... it flew right over my place and when it passed my roof i ran inside looking for my camrea or binoclulars about thirty seconds later i ran to my front of the house and watched the object slowly fly over the austin downtown area....i notice other small planes in the same skyline and the sun reflected on them this object moved like a plane, you know in a straight line and seemed to follow the 35 hwy that runs thru town.. i watch the skys often this was somthing that honestly looked manmade.. im just wondering if anyone saw or knows if the city has some unmanned servalence equip.
